io of 4.5:1 for textual elements (i.e. texts), and 3:1 for non-textual elements (i.e. link’s chevron).","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"However it is higly recommended for mobile devices to reach AAA level because of the screen sizes and luminosity issues, i.e. 7:1 for textual","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and 4.5:1 for non-textual elements.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"This utility helps to define wether a set of contrast ratio matches AA and AAA or not.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"See for example ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/system.design.orange.com\/0c1af118d\/p\/2531b9-accessibility-compliance","type":"reference"}],"role":"symbol","type":"topic"},"https://system.design.orange.com/0c1af118d/p/2531b9-accessibility-compliance":{"identifier":"https:\/\/system.design.orange.com\/0c1af118d\/p\/2531b9-accessibility-compliance","titleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"the following guidelines"}],"url":"https:\/\/system.design.orange.com\/0c1af118d\/p\/2531b9-accessibility-compliance","title":"the following guidelines","type":"link"}}}